g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔理個律師咩底都好, 而家搞到咁大都係多得佢個仔<br />\n自己tweet哂出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}